name: Espolex® WT557A
description:
Espolex® WT557A is a thermoplastic elastomer with superior low-temperature ductility. It is used for various applications such as air bag covers, painted applications, and injection molded parts. This product is suitable for Injection molding.

 

Applications:


Airbag Covers
Painted applications
Interior Trim
Handle Grips


 

Features:


Superior low-temperature ductility 


 

Benefits:


High performance from a mechanical property standpoint.
